Hibouk (O,O) Installation
=========================

Server configuration
--------------------

Hibouk works only on PHP 5.3 and upper.

This php extensions should be installed :
	dom, gd, json, libxml, pcre, PDO, pdo_mysql, SimpleXML, session, xsl, zip.

Hibouk supports mysql 4.0+.


Installation
------------

- Unzip the archive.
- Set write access on Hibouk directory, for apache.
- Go to Hibouk directory width your browser and click button right (preferences)
  to access connexion pannel :
  - Login : login
  - Password : password
- Set informations to connect and create database.


Importation files
-----------------

To import files .doc, .docx, .rtf and txt ; "LibreOffice" and "unoconv" must be installed.

LibreOffice: <http://www.libreoffice.org/>
unoconv: <https://github.com/dagwieers/unoconv>
